author: brane
msg: On the pin-externals branch: Fix a bug and an inefficiency.
(make_external_description): Do not generate invalid externals references
when the externals item has a revision string. Before this fix, the
generated -rX was not followed by a space.
(pin_externals_prop): Do not look up the same target in the
externals_to_pin hash on every iteration; do it just once per call,
since the local_abspath_or_url parameter does not change.
